title: About
main_content: SPS is run by students like you! Our committees are open to everyone to join. Officers Troy Tsubota & Michelle Dong, presidents Rainer Reczek & Sanjit Shirol, VPs Xing Liu, treasurer Nadia Sun, socials chair Kailash Ranganathan & Shaurya Jain, competitions chair Smridhi Mahajan, outreach chair Nico Rowland & Kaelani Adcock, projects chairs Ro’aa Alkhawaja & Yaamini Jois, equity and inclusion chairs Drey Crockett & Keshav Deoskar, seminars chairs Brandon Park & Kai Suwandi, media chairs Josh Zhang & Kevin Hernandez, grillmasters Adarsh Iyer, webmaster Kenneth Ng & Thien Kim Le, senior advisors
